=== Vim command-line ===

If X Window System support is not needed, install {{Package|app-editors/vim}}:

{{Emerge|app-editors/vim}}

=== Vim GUI ===

To install Vim with both the ncurses-based interface ({{Path|/usr/bin/vim}}) as well as the graphical interface (for the X Window System - {{Path|/usr/bin/gvim}}), install {{Package|app-editors/gvim}}:

{{Emerge|app-editors/gvim}}

There is also an experimental [[Qt]] interface called {{Package|app-editors/vim-qt}} which can also be installed.

=== Расширения ===

Категория ''app-vim'' содержит множество дополнительных спецификаций синтаксиса, плагинов и прочих относящихся к Vim вещей.

Используйте <tt>emerge</tt> или <tt>eix</tt>, чтобы получить обзор существующих пакетов в категории ''app-vim'':

{{Cmd|emerge --search "%@^app-vim"
|eix -cC app-vim}}

== Configuration ==

Vim can be configured on a per-user basis or through a system-wide configuration file. 

The system wide settings are set in {{Path|/etc/vim/vimrc}} whereas the user-specific configuration is located inside the user's home directory at {{Path|~/.vimrc}}.

